data.description: This gem is tucked away at the back of this neighborhood that offers easy access for trails to the Lynn Haven Bayou Park.  A neighborhood pool can appease the kids on those hot summer days and opportunities for kayaking along the Bayou are close at hand.  Features include an open floor plan, split bedroom plan, a hot tub for relaxing, and so convenient to schools, shopping and of course, our sugar white sands on the Gulf are close for your beach time fun.  Call today to schedule your private showing.
